item.title: 【Helpdesk】tutorial request: creating a live audio album
item.description: Hi! So many of you make such good live audio albums from concerts/video files. I have made a few before but the audio quality is not always super HQ, the volume is very low compared to streaming services (so I have to change audio volume of your speaker/headphone every time..) so I was wondering if you could tell me and everyone else on this great site what software you use/what steps you do? Maybe there is like a tutorial link somewhere already? Would be amazing, the more people create content the better in my opinion. thanks
item.author: downloadpop
